{
  "texts": [
    "Each variant is stored and documented, with details regarding the expected improvements.",
    "The Execution Agent runs modified versions of the system, executing the newly generated variants and collecting performance data for subsequent evaluation.",
    "It ensures that agents perform their tasks as specified in the new configuration and debug issues as they arise.",
    "The Execution Agent tracks qualitative and quantitative outputs, feeding this information into the evaluation process.",
    "The Evaluation Framework is responsible for assessing the outputs of each system variant."
  ]
}